{"tid":1463040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家呢一刻 我地應該將個訴求改做要求解放軍入城","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:35:09.000Z","uid":31249,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5340834c4daf3d2c448826d548827cbd61c4b11","tid":1463040,"uid":31249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"經過咗811 大家都睇到警方行使既暴力去到咩程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港市民已經對於香港警察維持治安既能力同自控能力完全失去信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該強烈要求中央政府派遣解放軍嚟香港維持秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />避免警察政府既形成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以發起遊行 口號改為要求解放軍代替香港警察維持治安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />表達我地既訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望特區政府同中央聆聽香港市民既訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我地亦都可以吸引到一班深藍絲加入我地既行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺鼓吹解放軍入城呢方面 我地係企喺同一陣線 加大我地既聲勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />減少社會紛爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想當年吳三桂引清兵入關 今日我地都可以做返同樣既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時會係解放軍同美軍鬥快入城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後我地既口號就改叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拯救香港！<br />\n老解入城！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5cf23a8c8f3dd2bbe78055c1f795f62047125af","tid":1463040,"uid":275447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"支持老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626dcd0b6da7ee2c3d750fee9b4604cc285c44b2","tid":1463040,"uid":24944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"究竟我哋係想以攬炒脅逼而贏<br />\n定純粹爭取攬炒<br />\n希望大家諗下"},{"pid":"0bb8cd531a2ecb4929da75c1805e6bde7fdf6bb4","tid":1463040,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9f4d6e6a56f95a90e0c4bf8530370d3fd86c6d","tid":1463040,"uid":275447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626dcd0b6da7ee2c3d750fee9b4604cc285c44b2","tid":1463040,"uid":24944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"究竟我哋係想以攬炒脅逼而贏<br />\n定純粹爭取攬炒<br />\n希望大家諗下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"如果唔爭取又點樣令政府覺得有威脅"},{"pid":"a269e5240de13ee7a2cc816ca37ecb168703d578","tid":1463040,"uid":224931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"頭先睇蘋果直播，<br />\n有班人喺禁區前面set防線，<br />\n仲要同啲旅客發生口角，<br />\n其實有冇需要做到咁呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>真係需要解釋畀旅客知係政府唔畀啲機起飛</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我真係諗唔明點解要阻止人入禁區"},{"pid":"339b2fc78fec8458eb48cd5a21a7b1233ab7183f","tid":1463040,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"本來想屌會失民意<br />\n但個原因係警犬不受控又ok"},{"pid":"3c20f16d4c9dac98abee2564214d9e73106db2ad","tid":1463040,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"行動po借位求推<br />\n816 經濟制裁 殺人政權(2) (附教學，後面精彩睇曬佢！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c64d7c57b0a50309fb20048711a12f4bd092430e","tid":1463040,"uid":275447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a269e5240de13ee7a2cc816ca37ecb168703d578","tid":1463040,"uid":224931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"頭先睇蘋果直播，<br />\n有班人喺禁區前面set防線，<br />\n仲要同啲旅客發生口角，<br />\n其實有冇需要做到咁呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span 